## Profile Delete

delete-q = kodi inuyo mukufuna titachosanso mawu amene mwalankhula, kapena tiwasunge mawuwo mu dataset
keep-info = Mawu anu amene mwalankhulawo tiwasunga mu dataset. Nthawi yomwe mungachise mbiri yanu simukwanitsa kupereka pempho lanu loti tichose mawu anu mu dataset
remove-info = Tidzawunikanso pempho lanu loti tichotse mawu anu ojambulidwa kuchokera mu deta. Ngati pempho lanu lavomerezedwa, tidzalankhula ndi omwe adatsitsa detayo ndikupempha kuti achotsenso mawu anu ojambulidwa.
why-delete-recordings =
    Zolemba za Common Voice zimagwiritsidwa ntchito ndi akatswiri a maphunziro, mabizinesi ang'onoang'ono, ndi okonda kuzindikira mawu kuti athandize kuphunzitsa ndi kukulitsa zinthu zomwe zimapezeka pagulu monga zitsanzo za mawu.
    
    Kodi mungatiuze chifukwa chake mukufuna kuti zolemba zanu zichotsedwe?
profile-form-delete = Musachotse mbiri yanu
